name: A Bird of II Feathers: White/Grey
description: All prices in Singapore dollars Estimated Price in USD$110, £70, €80, AUD$105 • H40cmx W42cm • Bleached heavy cotton and grey canvas • Embroidered features • Crafted with care to ensure a quality you will treasure • Packed in a self-made String tie envelope A Bird of II Feathers is a reversible bag that changes with your whim and fancy. Swan or cygnet. Elegant or beguiling. You decide what your bag says about you. Conceptualized and designed by Mimipong, A Bird of II Feathers is pattern cut and constructed by fashion and costume designer Hirochika Kameyama in Japan and finally put together by a skilled tailor. More than 10 prototypes were produced in this year long production before completion. Produced in a limited quantity More images here
